subject: Olympic Games (2010)
Bobsledding
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: The Jamaican national bobsled team, which gained acclaim in its Winter Olympics debut at Calgary in 1988 and spawned a Disney movie, did not qualify a sled for the Vancouver Games.
